# Email Parser Skill

## Description
This skill enables AI agents to parse and extract structured information from raw email data.

## Capabilities
- Extract sender information (name, email address)
- Parse subject lines and identify key topics
- Separate email body from signatures and replies
- Extract dates, times, and deadlines
- Identify recipients (To, CC, BCC)
- Parse attachments metadata

## Implementation Example
def parse_email(raw_email):
    """
    Extract key components from an email
    
    Args:
        raw_email (str): Raw email content
        
    Returns:
        dict: Structured email data
    """
    parsed_data = {
        'sender': extract_sender(raw_email),
        'recipients': extract_recipients(raw_email),
        'subject': extract_subject(raw_email),
        'body': extract_body(raw_email),
        'attachments': extract_attachments(raw_email),
        'date': extract_date(raw_email),
        'thread_id': extract_thread_id(raw_email)
    }
    return parsed_data

